[POSITION]475,32
[DIMENSION]310,250
[HINT]418,569,483,592

[MESSAGE]There's something you should know about the speed settings and how time passes in the restaurant universe. In order to progress faster, a month's time is simulated based on your restaurant's performance at the end of the first day of each month.

_Left-click_ on the _Next_ button to continue.
